Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.jupiter.integration.properties

Enum RefreshEachTimeBefore

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RefreshEachTimeBefore>
      • ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.jupiter.integration.properties.RefreshEachTimeBefore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<RefreshEachTimeBefore>
    public enum RefreshEachTimeBefore
extends Enum<RefreshEachTimeBefore>
    This enum is designed to define the strategy of the invoking of ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() by engines of TestNg. It is supposed to be invoked before methods annotated by BeforeAll and/or BeforeEach and/or Test/TestFactory/TestTemplate.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      ALL_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() each time before the first BeforeAll - method of a class is run.
      EACH_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() each time before the first method annotated by BeforeEach is run before any test.
      TEST_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() each time before any method annotated by Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate is run.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ALL_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore ALL_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() each time before the first BeforeAll - method of a class is run.

        Rule:

        ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() is invoked when:

        1. ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() has not been invoked before any BeforeAll/BeforeEach/Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate-method.

      • EACH_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore EACH_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() each time before the first method annotated by BeforeEach is run before any test.

        Rule:

        ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() is invoked when:

        1. ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() has not been invoked before some BeforeAll/BeforeEach-method and any Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate-method has not been invoked yet.

        2. ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() has not been invoked before some BeforeEach-method and any Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate-method has not been invoked yet.

      • TEST_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore TEST_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() each time before any method annotated by Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate is run.

        Rule:

        ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() is invoked when:

        1. ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() has not been invoked before some BeforeAll/BeforeEach-method and any Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate-method has not been invoked yet.

        2. ContextRefreshable.refreshContext() has not been invoked before some BeforeEach-method and any Test or TestFactory or TestTemplate-method has not been invoked yet.
